	# binary at arm's length, so the ocrs/rten engine and the CC-BY-SA-4.0 ocrs models are confined
	# here, off the permissive plugin's side of the boundary. Source-only like host-reference; the
	# reproducible-build provenance lands with the spec-and-release task.
